channel.title: [562/659] Project DungeonFest Release! [PDF] Version 1!
channel.description:
Before i Get into giving you guys the source and client package for version 1, i would like to state that no this is not a leech of the 657 that was released earlier today if you do not believe me then visit my development topic here: http://www.moparisthebest.com/smf/index.php/topic,510152.0.html Notice that the date is august 8th, The reason I am releasing are these reasons: School is starting, and two I have a lot of catching up to do on runescape.
So please enjoy this and You may possibly be able to persuade me not to quit rsps's, it's really up to you guys if i do or do not, Source and Client Package for Version One: [url=http://uppit.com/e8ech8ct8oye/PDF_Source_and_Client_Package!.rar]http://uppit.com/e8ech8ct8oye/PDF_Source_and_Client_Package!.rar[/url]
Please Enjoy these pictures: [IMG]http://i1087.photobucket.com/albums/j472/austincadle/proof.png[/img] Also I have added correct ags special, and more, such as korasi special, also i have added the abyssal vine whip, code is 21371, i have also added an amazing special attack that i think everyone will like! :) Also you need either 80, or 85 attack to weild :). [IMG]http://i1087.photobucket.com/albums/j472/austincadle/abbyvinewhip.png[/img] Here is a picture of the amazing custom special attack that I added myself! :): [IMG]http://i1087.photobucket.com/albums/j472/austincadle/customspecial.png[/img] Real working ags special! :): [IMG]http://i1087.photobucket.com/albums/j472/austincadle/realworkingagsspecial.png[/img] Working Korasi SPecial code is 19780 :): [IMG]http://i1087.photobucket.com/albums/j472/austincadle/korasispecialworking.png[/img] Not enough tokens to buy, and it recognizes that!, also buy 5 glitch has been fixed! :): [IMG]http://i1087.photobucket.com/albums/j472/austincadle/notenoughtokens.png[/img] Brand new Home! That's right new Draynor! :): [IMG]http://i1087.photobucket.com/albums/j472/austincadle/NewHome.png[/img] And Last But Certainly not Least, This Picture Shows how to pickup your loot, and shows that warrior guild tokens are dropped from all npc's ranging from 1-10, and godwars bosses 1-25! ALSO WHEN you get 99 dungeoneering you get the cape, hood, and (t) dungeoneering cape automatically to your bank! So please enjoy! :): [IMG]http://i1087.photobucket.com/albums/j472/austincadle/loot.png[/img]
Thanks for being such a great community MoparScape I will surely miss all of you, if I quit! Also I have also added the correct defender animations, and got rid of that gay old korasi hit, so please enjoy! :)
Downloads 25 50 100 200 250 350 500 750 1000 1250 1500 1650 2000 3000 4000
Fixing Cache Errors: http://up.ht/GGLPan
replace that with your existing clientsettings.java file.
